In Thailand, the largest lending store operator, EasyMoney, has seen a 20% increase in the number of customers using its stores over the past few months.
ValueMax, which operates the store in Bendemeer and 15 other stores like this in Singapore, plans to expand not only in neighboring Malaysia – where it already has four stores – but also outside of Asia, says Yeah Lee Ching, its CEO.
